snippet.title: World of Warcraft: Legion Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description: The Burning Legion’s assault on Azeroth launches next summer. Get an early look at the coming invasion in the World of Warcraft: Legion opening cinematic. For more info on the game, or to join the beta, head to http://wowlegion.com.
